column1: Includes Amazon Marketplace, Fulfilment by Amazon (FBA), and Amazon Webstore transactions
All amounts in GBP, unless specified
Sales tax collected: Includes sales tax collected from buyers for product sales, delivery, and gift wrap.
Selling fees: Includes variable closing fees and referral fees.
Other transaction fees: Includes delivery chargebacks, delivery holdbacks.
Other: Includes non-order transaction amounts. For more details, see the "Type" and "Description" columns for each order ID.
